                <h4>Children & Education</h4>
                <p>United’s commitment to the betterment of children from an overall wellbeing and educational standpoint has long been evident. Through volunteerism, fundraising and corporate support, United is a dedicated partner in education, supporter of afterschool programs and community outreach leader. Our presence can be seen in schools throughout our footprint, and felt though the positive impact of our fundraising events, such as the Kids Golf Classic and the Washington Jesuit Academy Gridiron Classic.</p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="services-detail">
