                <p>United understands the health challenges our communities face and we respond through fundraising and corporate support. United’s commitment to community health care is vividly on display with our hosting and sponsorship of the United Cardinal Classic Golf Tournament to benefit the INOVA® Kellar Center. We are particularly responsive to the market-specific health and wellness needs throughout our footprint.</p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="services-detail">
