                <h4>Affordable Housing</h4>
                <p>United is committed to providing access to affordable housing to individuals and families in the communities we serve. Through robust relationships with affordable housing developers, community development lending expertise, and strong partnership with the Federal Home Loan Bank (FHLB), United is able to provide flexible and responsive financing solutions for projects that provide affordable, transitional and emergency housing.</p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="services-detail">
                <img src="images/icons8-hotel-star-50.png" alt="illustration">
                <h4>Economic Vitality</h4>
                <p>United recognizes the importance of thriving communities. We build strong relationships with organizations that support the viability of the communities we serve. Being actively involved in local economic development is not only essential, but also leads to opportunities to offer professional assistance or financing for projects that will catalyze positive change in our company’s footprint.  We partner with urban redevelopment authorities, regional planning commissions, small business incubators and chambers of commerce. In addition, we provide innovative, flexible and responsive products and services to people and businesses in our communities to best meet their needs.</p>
